From the Infowars web site ::

On the Wednesday edition of the Alex Jones Show, Alex talks with syndicated radio talk show host and national television personality Lionel, who will touch on a number of issues, including the OWS movement and recent actions by the Obama administration. 

Alex covers the latest breaking news, including the EU debt crisis now reaching terminal velocity. He will also talk about street lights with Homeland Security applications and the government takeover of the Emergency Alert System and a nationwide test of the system next month.  

Today's broadcast included an "overdrive" segment of approximately 30 minutes.
